 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

						  FROM fs_banners AS a
						  WHERE published = 1
						  AND category_id IN (43) AND (listItemid = 'all'
							OR listItemid like '%,1,%')
							 ORDER BY ordering, id

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

SELECT id,title,content, ordering, module, position, showTitle, params ,listItemid,news_categories,contents_categories,link_title
						FROM fs_blocks AS a 
						WHERE published = 1 
					ORDER BY ordering

time:::0.00099992752075195

===========

 SELECT *
					  FROM fs_products_categories
					  WHERE published = 1 AND is_special = 1

time:::0

===========

 SELECT id,name, alias,tags_group,tablename,is_accessories, root_id, is_accessories,list_parents,icon,is_special
					FROM fs_products_categories 
					WHERE 
						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0
					ORDER BY ordering
							

time:::0

===========

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

time:::0.00099992752075195

===========

 SELECT id,name, image, alias
							FROM fs_manufactories 
							WHERE published = 1  
							 AND tablenames like "%,fs_products_tai_nghe,%"
							 ORDER BY  ordering ASC,name ASC
							 

time:::0.0010001659393311

===========

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%2%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT name,id,category_id,type,image,flash,content,link,height,width
						  FROM fs_banners AS a
						  WHERE published = 1
						  AND category_id IN (43) AND (listItemid = 'all'
							OR listItemid like '%,1,%')
							 ORDER BY ordering, id 

time:::0.00099992752075195

						  FROM fs_strengths
						 WHERE  published = 1 
						 ORDER BY  ordering ASC 
						 LIMIT 4

 SELECT title,alias,image,summary,hits,updated_time,id,category_alias,is_hot,comments_total,created_time
						  FROM fs_news
						 WHERE  published = 1 and category_published = 1 
						  ORDER BY   ordering DESC,created_time DESC, ordering DESC,created_time DESC
						 LIMIT 4  
						 

time:::0.0010001659393311

===========

 SELECT *
					FROM fs_menus_items
					WHERE published  = 1
						AND group_id = 3 
					ORDER BY ordering

time:::0.00099992752075195

===========

 SELECT id, name, level, alias,is_bold,link
					FROM fs_tags
					WHERE published  = 1  
					ORDER BY ordering
					LIMIT 150

					FROM fs_products_categories 
					WHERE 
						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0
					ORDER BY ordering

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%4%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

						FROM fs_blocks AS a 
						WHERE published = 1 
					ORDER BY ordering

 SELECT id,name, alias,tags_group,tablename,is_accessories, root_id, is_accessories,list_parents,icon,is_special
					FROM fs_products_categories 
					WHERE 
						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0
					ORDER BY ordering
							

time:::0.00099992752075195

===========

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

time:::0.00099992752075195

===========

 SELECT id,name, image, alias
							FROM fs_manufactories 
							WHERE published = 1  
							 AND tablenames like "%,fs_products_tai_nghe,%"
							 ORDER BY  ordering ASC,name ASC
							 

time:::0.00099992752075195

						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1

						 LIMIT 10

						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name, alias,tags_group,tablename,is_accessories, root_id, is_accessories,list_parents,icon,is_special
					FROM fs_products_categories 
					WHERE 
						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0
					ORDER BY ordering
							

time:::0.0010001659393311

===========

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

							FROM fs_manufactories 
							WHERE published = 1  
							 AND tablenames like "%,fs_products_loa_di_dong,%"
							 ORDER BY  ordering ASC,name ASC

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%3%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

						FROM fs_blocks AS a 
						WHERE published = 1

 SELECT id,name, alias,tags_group,tablename,is_accessories, root_id, is_accessories,list_parents,icon,is_special
					FROM fs_products_categories 
					WHERE 
						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0
					ORDER BY ordering
							

time:::0

===========

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

time:::0.00099992752075195

===========

							 ORDER BY  ordering ASC,name ASC

						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%3%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

time:::0

===========

						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%2%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10
